      "title": "Personal Injury Law in Maryland | Statute of Limitations, Settlement Ranges & Rights",
      "description": "Complete guide to personal injury law in Maryland. Statute of limitations, negligence rules, average settlements, and what to do after an accident.",
      "readTime": "15 min",
