      "question": "What is a disfigurement injury and what is the settlement?",
      "title": "What is a disfigurement injury and what is the settlement? | Personal Injury Guide",
      "description": "Understand disfigurement injuries, their impact on personal injury claims, and how settlements are determined. Learn about compensation for physical and emotional damages.",
      "readTime": "10 min",
