      "question": "What is the statute of limitations in my state?",
      "title": "What is the statute of limitations in my state? | Personal Injury Guide",
      "description": "Understand the statute of limitations in personal injury cases, a critical legal deadline that varies by state and impacts your right to compensation.",
      "readTime": "8 min",
      "author": "Personal Injury Attorneys at www.CasePort.io",
